# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Docker Ignore - Monorepo
# Excludes files not needed in Docker build context
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Dependencies (installed fresh in container)
node_modules
**/node_modules

# Build outputs (rebuilt in container)
.next
**/.next
dist
**/dist
.turbo
**/.turbo

# Development files
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Environment files (secrets - never include!)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# IDE and editor
.idea
.vscode
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Git
.git
.gitignore

# Docker files (no need to copy these into build)
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# Documentation
*.md
!README.md
docs

# Testing
coverage
**/.coverage
.nyc_output
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
__tests__
**/__tests__

# CI/CD
.github
.gitlab-ci.yml
.circleci

# Misc
.claude
*.tgz
*.tar.gz
